WAY 4: H4 REFRACTIONS
========================================================================

K_H4 = Z/M* = 15/(12/11) = 15*11/12 = 55/4 = 13.7500000000  EXACT
Verify: 15*11/12 = 13.7500000000  Match: True

f_H4 = pi^2*11/120 = 0.904713736766525
  Derived: pi = (12/11)*(10/pi)*f_H4  =>  f_H4=pi^2*11/120
  Verify v_g/c = (12/11)*(10/pi)*f_H4 = 3.141592653589793
  pi                                   = 3.141592653589793
  Match (error<1e-14): True

NOTE: f_H4=pi^2*11/120=0.9047 (NOT 0.8976).
  2*pi/7=0.8976 is the vertex angle (distinct). Prior memo stated 0.897539 (error).

gamma_1 = pi/10 = 0.314159265358979
  CORRECTION (Lemma 7.6 v1.7): gamma_1=pi/10. Prior M8-series had gamma_1=pi/12.

4 Physical Predictions from K_H4=13.75:
  1. G_eff = G_0 * K_H4 = 13.75 * G_0
  2. Delta_tau_H4 = 1.89m / (c/13.75) = 86.6828 ns
  3. Routes max = 35 * K_H4/10 = 48.125  -> 48 routes
  4. ebits min  = 2800/K_H4 = 203.6364  -> 204 ebits

Self-Duality Proof:
  M* = 600/550 = 12/11  (550 = 600 - 600/12)
  K_H4 = Z/M* = 15/(12/11) = 55/4 = 13.75  QED
  600/120=5  1200/720=5/3  (duality ratios)

